data.description: Introducing 4750 Oakmont St: A Well-Kept 3-Bedroom Home with Endless Potential  Welcome to 4750 Oakmont St, a charming and well-maintained residence offering 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. This home is in good condition, with a warm ambiance and plenty of natural light. The spacious bedrooms provide comfortable retreats. Located on Oakmont St, it enjoys a convenient neighborhood with nearby amenities, including shops, parks, and schools, adding to the convenience and quality of life. Don't miss the opportunity to transform this house into your dream home. Schedule a showing today at 4750 Oakmont St and envision the possibilities that await you.
